Committee composition: Appropriate and expert-based under the scheme for selection of incentive factories.
Scrutiny will be done by a two-tier committee to ensure evaluation.
The composition of the Scrutiny Committee and Selection Committee to select the awardees is as follows: -
A representative from Vasantdada Sugar Institute (VSI), Pune
A representative of the Maharashtra State Cooperative Sugar Factories Association (Sugar Union)
Two independent experts in the sugar industry in the economy, engineering, or agriculture
Each Regional Joint Director has 3 co-operative factories and 3 private units of excellence in their respective departments.
